CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777107988
OL,3,CAssisted dying bill fails after
OL,4,Crunning out of time in House of Lords
OL,6,FParalympian Baroness Tanni Grey-
OL,7,FThompson, who had spoken out against
OL,8,Fthe bill, said it had failed because
OL,9,F"there are too many gaps in it" adding
OL,10,Fthat she felt there was "a lot of
OL,11,Fmisunderstanding about what people
OL,12,Fmight get" under a law change.
OL,14,FThose opposed to the bill have branded
OL,15,Fit "unsafe and unworkable" and "bad
OL,16,Flaw", citing their concerns around
OL,17,Fpotential coercion of vulnerable
OL,18,Fpeople and a lack of safeguards for
OL,19,Fthose with disabilities.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@_O]rD@YOUtD@JO]wD@DOUwD@ZO]wD@
OL,26,A`OUxD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
