PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777107988
OL,3,CAssisted dying bill fails after
OL,4,Crunning out of time in House of Lords
OL,6,FBaroness Campbell of Surbiton, a
OL,7,Fformer commissioner at Britain's
OL,8,Frights watchdog the Equality and Human
OL,9,FRights Commission (EHRC), said
OL,10,Fdisabled people had contacted her to
OL,11,Fsay this "particular bill frightens
OL,12,Fthem, and they want me to explain to
OL,13,Fyour Lordships why it is dangerous for
OL,14,Fthem".
OL,26,@sD@JOUvD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
