CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777107988
OL,3,CAssisted dying bill fails after
OL,4,Crunning out of time in House of Lords
OL,6,FThe crossbench peer, who has spinal
OL,7,Fmuscular atrophy, and addressed the
OL,8,Fchamber remotely, said disabled people
OL,9,F"fear unequal access to care shaping
OL,10,Ftheir choices, they fear subtle
OL,11,Fcoercion that cannot be easily
OL,12,Fdetected".
OL,14,FConservative former deputy prime
OL,15,Fminister Baroness Therese Coffey said
OL,16,Fshe feared "that many peers and many
OL,17,FMPs are putting choice for some ahead
OL,18,Fof concern on coercion for others".
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@IO]xD@LOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
