CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777107988
OL,3,CAssisted dying bill fails after
OL,4,Crunning out of time in House of Lords
OL,6,FLord Falconer said many terminally ill
OL,7,Fpeople and their relatives "who have
OL,8,Fshown such courage and forbearance"
OL,9,Fhave been "utterly bewildered by the
OL,10,Fway we (peers) have behaved".
OL,12,FSupporters have vowed to try to bring
OL,13,Fthe bill back at the next
OL,14,Fparliamentary session, with its
OL,15,Fsponsor in the Commons Kim Leadbeater
OL,16,F` who watched proceedings from the
OL,17,Fgallery on Friday ` saying she will
OL,18,Fagain enter her name in the ballot of
OL,19,Fprivate members' bills.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@cO]qD@KOUrD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
