PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777107988
OL,3,CAssisted dying bill fails after
OL,4,Crunning out of time in House of Lords
OL,6,FCampaigners have said they could use
OL,7,Fthe Parliament Act to get the bill
OL,8,Fthrough if it was selected.
OL,10,FThat act, a rarely used piece of
OL,11,Flegislation, allows for bills that
OL,12,Fhave been backed by the Commons in two
OL,13,Fsuccessive sessions but rejected by
OL,14,Fpeers to pass into law without Lords
OL,15,Fapproval.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
