OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777107988
OL,3,CAssisted dying bill fails after
OL,4,Crunning out of time in House of Lords
OL,6,FLord Falconer told peers: "It is clear
OL,7,Fthat the issue will not go away, nor
OL,8,Fshould it, until it is resolved.
OL,9,FParliament can and must come to a
OL,10,Fdecision. It is now for the other
OL,11,Fplace to decide what we do next."
OL,13,FDame Sarah Mullally, the most senior
OL,14,Fbishop in the Church of England and a
OL,15,Fformer chief nurse, said if the bill
OL,16,Fcomes back, "we need to do our work
OL,17,Fdifferently".
OL,26,@nD@[OUsD@aO]xD@MOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
