PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1777107988
OL,3,CAssisted dying bill fails after
OL,4,Crunning out of time in House of Lords
OL,6,FHe said it was "known that the Prime
OL,7,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer supported
OL,8,Fit", and suggested Bill supporters
OL,9,Fwere "standing at the entrance to the
OL,10,Flobbies taking note of who was going
OL,11,Fthrough".
OL,13,FHe added: "I'm just passing on what
OL,14,FLabour MPs have said to me, that they
OL,15,Ffelt intimidated."
OL,26,@nD@POUpD@CO]qD@FOUsD@HO]uD@KOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
