OL,3,CAssisted dying bill fails after
OL,4,Crunning out of time in House of Lords
OL,6,FSpeaking to broadcasters on a visit to
OL,7,FSwindon, she suggested the government
OL,8,Fhad "used a private members' Bill to
OL,9,Fpush through its agenda" and said
OL,10,Fthere were "all sorts of problems"
OL,11,Fwith the legislation.
OL,13,FShe said: "It's something that Keir
OL,14,FStarmer wants to see. He said he made
OL,15,Fa promise to Esther Rantzen. I think
OL,16,Fhe should focus on the rest of the
OL,17,Fcountry."
OL,26,@pD@EOUqD@XO]rD@LOUrD@bO]uD@KOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
